[bold]Nominators:[/bold]
[bullet]
[bullet]
[bullet]
[color=Gray]It is recommended that the appointee be nominated by at least two existing members of Station Command. It is highly recommended against appointing a crew member who has not been nominated by another member of station command. Nominators of non-command members that are in the department of the appointed position can also be listed here. It is recommended against to appoint a crew member who has not been nominated by any department members of the appointed position.[/color]

[bold]Primary Qualifications[/bold]
[color=Grey]Describe the main reasons why this crew member was nominated and chosen for the appointment.[/color]
